relevant_findings.HEENT: PERRL, EOMI. No scleral icterus. No conjunctival injection. Mucous membranes moist. No oral ulcers.
relevant_findings.Neck: Supple, no lymphadenopathy, no JVP elevation.
relevant_findings.Lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi. Normal respiratory effort.
relevant_findings.Cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops.
relevant_findings.Abdomen: Soft, significant right lower quadrant tenderness to palpation (light), positive epigastric tenderness, right upper quadrant tenderness, faint right flank tenderness, no clear right costovertebral angle tenderness, non-distended, positive bowel sounds.
relevant_findings.Extremities: Warm and well perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing, or edema. Dorsalis pedis pulses mildly diminished bilaterally.
relevant_findings.Neurological: Alert and oriented to person, place, and time, cranial nerves intact.
